## Flags

| Flag | Description |
|------|-------------|
| `--date YYYY-MM-DD` | Generate for specific date |
| `--yesterday` | Include yesterday in "Yesterday" section |
| `--no-toggl` | Skip Toggl time tracking |
| `--no-linear` | Skip Linear issues |
| `--repos path` | Custom repos path (default: ~/code) |

## Notes

- **Slack MCP Deferred**: Currently outputs for manual copy-paste. When Slack MCP is enabled, can add `--post` flag to send directly.
- **Timezone**: Uses system timezone for date calculations.
- **Privacy**: Only shows your commits/issues (uses git config user.email).

